<07-20-98> v3.2.08 - TSE Pro/32 v2.8
Replaces v3.2.01 dated 03-12-98.
Split & Scroll (SAS) Macro v3.2.08
Description: Splits the display into windows
for each file opened.  Allows simultaneous
horizontal and vertical key and auto
scrolling of the windows.  Fully configurable
scrolling. Scroll a number lines at a time.
Different menu modes.  Menu or Key driven.
Please read the included SAS.txt file for
more detailed information.  Author: Alex S
Wilson (alex.s.wilson@btinternet.com)
